CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 15, 1952, pg. 10 reads: "Holy Cross Throng - A general view of the throng of card players who enjoyed the tremendously successful card party given Tuesday night at the Chatham Street YWCA. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of men, and women, including one wearing light colored dress and light colored headpiece, seated at card tables in Chatham Street YWCA for Church of the Holy Cross card party
